"title": "1085: God, love of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1085",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The deepest possible expression of God's character. Though God loves all people, he is especially committed to sacrificial, loyal relationships with his people.</p>\n<h2>God's nature is love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:8\">1JN 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:16\">1JN 4:16</a></p>\n<h3>His love is perfectly expressed within the Trinity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:10-Mark1:11\">MRK 1:10–1:11</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:16-Matt3:17\">MAT 3:16–3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:21-Luke3:22\">LUK 3:21–3:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:20\">JHN 5:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:17\">JHN 10:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:6\">EPH 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:13\">COL 1:13</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of God's love</h2>\n<h3>It is eternal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:3\">JER 31:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:17\">PSA 103:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:1-Ps136:26\">PSA 136:1–136:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:15-Isa49:16\">ISA 49:15–49:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:8\">ISA 54:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:10\">ISA 54:10</a></p>\n<h3>It is a covenant love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9\">DEU 7:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:6\">EXO 20:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:10\">DEU 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:12\">DEU 7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:23\">1KI 8:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:14\">2CH 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:45\">PSA 106:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:4\">DAN 9:4</a></p>\n<h3>It is lavish</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6-Exod34:7\">EXO 34:6–34:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:17\">NEH 9:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:8\">PSA 103:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:13\">JOL 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">JON 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>It is holy and just</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:5\">PSA 33:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:28\">PSA 37:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:4\">PSA 99:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:8\">ISA 61:8</a></p>\n<h2>Images of God's love</h2>\n<p>God as a father:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:31\">DEU 1:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1-Hos11:4\">HOS 11:1–11:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:11-Luke15:32\">LUK 15:11–15:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:6\">HEB 12:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:12\">PRO 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:32\">JER 31:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:14-Hos2:20\">HOS 2:14–2:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2\">REV 21:2</a></p>\n<h2>God's loving actions</h2>\n<h3>The gift of God's Son is a unique act of love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:9-1John4:10\">1JN 4:9–4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:13\">JHN 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:7-Rom5:8\">ROM 5:7–5:8</a></p>\n<h3>God sets his love on the unlovely</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:7-Deut7:8\">DEU 7:7–7:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:1-Ezek16:14\">EZK 16:1–16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8\">ROM 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>God always acts in love towards believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:14\">2CO 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:3\">2JN 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>God's love for his people</h2>\n<h3>Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:4\">ISA 43:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:15\">DEU 10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:8\">2CH 9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:24\">MAT 15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:15-Rom9:16\">ROM 9:15–9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19\">EXO 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:28\">ROM 11:28</a></p>\n<h3>The church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5\">REV 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:27\">JHN 16:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:23\">JHN 17:23</a></p>\n<h2>God's love for the world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:18\">DEU 10:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16-John3:17\">JHN 3:16–3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:9\">PSA 145:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:17\">PSA 145:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">MAT 5:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:25\">ACT 17:25</a></p>\n<h2>God's love for individuals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:24-2Sam12:25\">2SA 12:24–12:25</a></strong> <em>“Jedidiah” means “loved by the LORD”.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:12\">DEU 33:12</a> <em>Benjamin</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:15\">2SA 7:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:13\">1CH 17:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:3\">ISA 55:3</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:28\">EZR 7:28</a> <em>Ezra</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:26\">NEH 13:26</a> <em>Solomon</em></p>\n<h2>God's love transforms human love</h2>\n<h3>Human love must respond to God's love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:19\">1JN 4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:6\">DEU 30:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1\">EPH 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12-Col3:14\">COL 3:12–3:14</a></p>\n<h3>Human love must be modelled on God's love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:44-Matt5:45\">MAT 5:44–5:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:1\">HOS 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15\">1JN 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7-1John4:8\">1JN 4:7–4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:11-1John4:12\">1JN 4:11–4:12</a></p>",
